# Enterprise SaaS Architecture

## Tenancy

Use `my add tenancy --mode <strategy>`:

| Mode | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `single-db` | Shared database with `tenant_id` column |
| `schema-per-tenant` | PostgreSQL schema per tenant |
| `db-per-tenant` | Isolated database per tenant |

## Modules

| Module | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| Organizations | `src/modules/organizations` | Tenant root entity |
| Teams | `src/modules/teams` | Team membership within orgs |
| Billing | `src/modules/billing` | Subscription & invoice scaffold |

## Compliance checklist

- [ ] Enable MFA for admin users (`my add auth` with MFA)
- [ ] Configure audit logging (`my add observability`)
- [ ] Set up secret management (see `ENVIRONMENT.md`)
- [ ] Enable dependency scanning (`.github/workflows/codeql.yml`)
